title: american horror story coven - misty day meets stevie nicks
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: Misty is literally me if I met Stevie.
i will never be over misty dying she deserved so much better
Who wouldn't faint upon walking into a room with Stevie Nicks in it?
who wouldn't faint with Jessica Lange and Stevie Nicks in the room you just walked into?

The creators of AHS obviously have major respect for Stevie Nicks, her inclusion in the show might be confusing to some but tbh as a long time Stevie nicks fan I'm so impressed and delighted that this was even a thing in the amazing world of AHS
